General.Name: USWE Sports AB
General.Description: Uswe Sports AB (publ) develops and produces outdoor equipment for the international sports and outdoor market. It offers backpacks, fluid backpacks, and waist belts, as well as VOID's cycling clothing. The company also provides hydration packs, daypacks, protector packs, moto packing, vests, hip packs, and apparels. The company provides its products for various sports activities, such as mountain biking, trail running, motorsports, and skiing. It also offers its products through its website and amazon. Uswe Sports AB (publ) was founded in 2007 and is based in Malmö, Sweden.
